label.value: Recurrence of CHAARTED Low Volume Metastatic Disease

value.value: A recurrence of low volume metastatic disease as defined by the CHAARTED Study (Chemohormonal Therapy Versus Androgen Ablation Randomized Trial for Extensive Disease in Prostate Cancer) as less than four bone metastases.
A recurrence of disease at the site of the primary prostatic lesion.

label.value: Recurrence of Primary in Seminal Vesicles
